biotools.summary: Synthetic Models of biological systems Generator (SMGen) automatically generates synthetic models of biochemical reaction networks that, by construction, are characterized by both features (e.g. system connectivity, reaction discreteness) and emergent dynamics \textcolor{red}{that do not exhaust all the reactants, a non-trivial behavior that often characterizes} real biochemical networks.
